p-is-layout-constrained\">\n<h1 class=\"wp-block-heading has-white-color has-text-color\">Embarquez dans mon univers num\u00e9rique, Romain Nguyen<\/h1>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-white-color has-text-color has-medium-font-size\" style=\"margin-top:16px\">Explorez l\u2019univers de l\u2019informatique \u00e0 travers ma vision, un \u00e9tudiant de Toulon passionn\u00e9 par les nouvelles technologies. Mon portfolio illustre mon parcours dans les services informatiques et ma d\u00e9termination \u00e0 exceller dans le domaine du r\u00e9seau.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons is-layout-flex wp-container-core-buttons-is-layout-1 wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex\" style=\"margin-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--40)\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-button is-style-fill\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link has-background-color has-text-color has-background has-link-color wp-element-button\" href=\"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/mon-cv\/\" style=\"border-radius:100px;background:linear-gradient(71deg,rgb(0,98,255) 0%,rgb(62,57,96) 100%)\">Mon CV<\/a><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignwide has-background-background-color has-background has-medium-font-size is-layout-constrained wp-container-core-group-is-layout-4 wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\" style=\"margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;padding-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--40);padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30);padding-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--40);padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--30)\">\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-center\">\u00c0 propos de moi ? <\/h3>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-center\">Quelles sont mes ambitions ?<\/h3>\n\n\n<style>.wp-block-kadence-spacer.kt-block-spacer-13_43dacb-d5 .kt-block-spacer{height:73px;}.wp-block-kadence-spacer.kt-block-spacer-13_43dacb-d5 .kt-divider{border-top-width:5px;height:1px;border-top-color:#0083ff;width:100%;border-top-style:solid;}<\/style>\n<div class=\"wp-block-kadence-spacer aligncenter kt-block-spacer-13_43dacb-d5\"><div class=\"kt-block-spacer kt-block-spacer-halign-center\"><hr class=\"kt-divider\"\/><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-medium-font-size\"><strong>Romain Nguyen<\/strong>, \u00e9tudiant d\u00e9termin\u00e9 en informatique, je saisis l&rsquo;innovation technologique \u00e0 travers mon travail. <strong>19 ans<\/strong> et actuellement en <strong>BTS (SIO)<\/strong>, Services Informatiques aux Organisations <strong>option (SISR)<\/strong>, Solutions d\u2019Infrastructure Syst\u00e8mes et R\u00e9seaux.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-medium-font-size\">Je suis d\u00e9termin\u00e9 \u00e0 aller au del\u00e0 de ma passion, afin de faire de l&rsquo;informatique mon m\u00e9tier.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-medium-font-size\">C&rsquo;est pour cela que j\u2019aimerais poursuivre mes \u00e9tudes en faisant, \u00e0 la fin de mon BTS, <strong>une licence professionnelle en Informatique<\/strong> afin d\u2019effectuer<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-medium-font-size\">par la suite un&nbsp;<strong>Mast\u00e8re professionnel manager en infrastructures et cybers\u00e9curit\u00e9 des SI en alternance<\/strong>, je l&rsquo;esp\u00e8re.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n\n<style>.kb-lottie-container13_f1f659-25{margin-top:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;}.kb-lottie-container13_f1f659-25 dotlottie-player{max-width:860px;}<\/style><div class=\"kb-lottie-container kb-lottie-container13_f1f659-25\"><dotlottie-player loop=\"true\" speed=\"1\" autoplay=\"true\" mode=\"normal\" src=\"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-json\/kb-lottieanimation\/v1\/animations\/28.json\"\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tid=\"kb-lottie-player13_f1f659-25\"\n\t\t\t\t\t\t><\/dotlottie-player><\/div>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull has-background-background-color has-background is-content-justification-center is-layout-constrained wp-container-core-group-is-layout-16 wp-block-group-is